  "detailed_description": "It's your time to begin the pilgrimage your ancestors have done for decades, will you be able to come back in one piece or will you perish along the way?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315570/extras/1032567731bfd1ab723f7480197faf2f.poster.avif?t=1721761696\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315570/extras/1032567731bfd1ab723f7480197faf2f.webm?t=1721761696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315570/extras/1032567731bfd1ab723f7480197faf2f.mp4?t=1721761696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Heirloom is a small 2D platformer inspired by retro games, 1bit and textmode art. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315570/extras/1bdaf84c58aa9396c400e6eda0a06c9c.poster.avif?t=1721761696\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315570/extras/1bdaf84c58aa9396c400e6eda0a06c9c.webm?t=1721761696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315570/extras/1bdaf84c58aa9396c400e6eda0a06c9c.mp4?t=1721761696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Run, jump and avoid obstacles through 4 simple but challenging levels. Explore a beautiful, hand-crafted pixel world. Meet captivating NPCs and venture up to the Old Summit and back to retrieve the family Heirloom. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315570/extras/f38f71bc6acc46ed41b72923863f2dba.poster.avif?t=1721761696\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315570/extras/f38f71bc6acc46ed41b72923863f2dba.webm?t=1721761696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315570/extras/f38f71bc6acc46ed41b72923863f2dba.mp4?t=1721761696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>5 unique areas to explore</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A peculiar ability to discover</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Death counter so you can keep track of all your failures</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Captivating NPCs</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A rich story unveiling the family tradition</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Old school CRT monitor effect</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Minimalist pixel art graphics</li></ul>",
